  "body": "In the typescript-support.ts file, there is some logic to determine if the typescript is supported by creating a list of all packages installed in ./node_modules and then seeing if they contain typescript and ts-node.\r\n\r\nWhile using yarn workspaces, some dependencies might be in a node_modules folder higher in the directory structure. \r\n\r\nA workaround is to configure nohoist:\r\n\r\n```\r\n  \"workspaces\": {\r\n    \"packages\": [\r\n      \"packages/*\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"nohoist\": [\r\n      \"**/@nomiclabs/**\",\r\n      \"**/typescript\",\r\n      \"**/ts-node\"\r\n    ]\r\n  },\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut it would be better if the list of packages also included the packages higher up in the tree.",
